+Sandboxing note: `agent.sandbox.mode: "non-main"` uses `session.mainKey` (default `"main"`),
+so group/channel sessions are sandboxed. If you want the main agent to always
+run on host, set an explicit per-agent override:
+
+```json
+{
+  "routing": {
+    "agents": {
+      "main": {
+        "workspace": "~/clawd",
+        "sandbox": { "mode": "off" }
+      }
+    }
+  }
+}
+```
